UPDATES = [
    {"file": "cpp-fundamentals.json", "title": "协程(Coroutines)与异步I/O在ROS2中的应用",
     "content": "### C++20协程简介\n\n协程(Coroutine)是可以暂停和恢复的函数。在机器人中，协程可以简化异步传感器读取和多任务协调的代码。\n\n### 协程 vs 线程\n\n| 特性 | 线程 | 协程 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 调度 | OS内核调度 | 用户态切换 |\n| 开销 | 创建~1MB栈 | 创建~100B |\n| 切换 | ~1us(上下文) | ~10ns |\n| 并发 | 真正并行 | 协作式并发 |\n| 适合 | CPU密集 | I/O密集 |\n\n```\n传统ROS2回调 (复杂):\n  void image_callback(msg) { process(msg); }  // 回调A\n  void lidar_callback(msg) { process(msg); }  // 回调B\n  void timer_callback() { control(); }         // 回调C\n  // 三个回调，状态管理混乱\n\n协程风格 (清晰):\n  co_await get_image();     // 暂停等待图像\n  co_await get_lidar();     // 暂停等待点云\n  compute_control();        // 计算控制\n  co_await send_command();  // 发送指令\n  // 顺序写法，编译器自动处理暂停/恢复\n```\n\n### 简单协程示例\n\n```cpp\n// C++20 协程 (概念演示)\n#include <coroutine>\n#include <iostream>\n\nstruct SensorData {\n    struct promise_type {\n        SensorData get_return_object() { return {}; }\n        std::suspend_never initial_suspend() { return {}; }\n        std::suspend_never final_suspend() noexcept { return {}; }\n        void return_void() {}\n        void unhandled_exception() {}\n    };\n};\n\n// 协程: 异步读取传感器\nSensorData async_read_sensor() {\n    // co_await read_camera();  // 暂停等待相机\n    // co_await read_imu();     // 暂停等待IMU\n    // process_data();          // 处理数据\n    co_return;\n}\n```\n\n```python\nimport asyncio\nimport time\n\n# Python 协程演示 (与C++20协程概念相同)\nasync def robot_control_loop():\n    '''协程风格的机器人控制循环'''\n    while True:\n        # 并发等待多个传感器\n        image, lidar, imu = await asyncio.gather(\n            read_camera(),\n            read_lidar(),\n            read_imu(),\n        )\n        # 所有数据到齐后处理\n        action = compute_action(image, lidar, imu)\n        await send_command(action)\n        await asyncio.sleep(0.02)  # 50Hz\n\nasync def read_camera():\n    await asyncio.sleep(0.033)  # 模拟30Hz相机\n    return 'image_frame'\n\nasync def read_lidar():\n    await asyncio.sleep(0.1)  # 模拟10Hz LiDAR\n    return 'pointcloud'\n\nasync def read_imu():\n    await asyncio.sleep(0.005)  # 模拟200Hz IMU\n    return 'imu_data'\n\ndef compute_action(img, pc, imu):\n    return [0.1] * 7\n\nasync def send_command(action):\n    await asyncio.sleep(0.001)\n\n# 运行3个控制周期\nasync def demo():\n    for i in range(3):\n        t0 = time.perf_counter()\n        img, lid, imu = await asyncio.gather(\n            read_camera(), read_lidar(), read_imu())\n        dt = (time.perf_counter() - t0) * 1000\n        print(f'Cycle {i+1}: all sensors ready in {dt:.1f}ms '\n              f'(最慢的lidar决定总时间)')\n\nasyncio.run(demo())\nprint('协程优势: 并发等待多传感器, 代码像顺序写法一样清晰')\n```\n\n### 练习\n1. 用C++20协程实现异步传感器读取Pipeline\n2. 对比回调式和协程式ROS2节点的代码复杂度\n3. 用Python asyncio实现多传感器并发读取+控制循环"},
    {"file": "multimodal-perception.json", "title": "触觉伺服：用触觉反馈引导精细操作",
     "content": "### 什么是触觉伺服？\n\n类似视觉伺服用图像反馈控制运动，**触觉伺服(Tactile Servoing)**用触觉传感器的反馈来引导机器人进行精细操作——特别是在视觉无法观测的场景（如手指下方被遮挡的接触面）。\n\n### 触觉伺服的优势场景\n\n```\n视觉看不到的:\n  - 手指下方的接触面 (被手指遮挡)\n  - 黑暗环境中的操作\n  - 高速接触的瞬态力\n\n需要力觉精度的:\n  - 插入装配 (peg-in-hole): 需要感知微小的接触力引导\n  - 表面跟随 (打磨/擦拭): 需要维持恒定法向力\n  - 材质识别: 通过触觉纹理判断物体\n```\n\n### GelSight触觉伺服\n\nGelSight通过光学测量弹性体形变，获得接触面的高分辨率3D形状：\n\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\nclass TactileServoController:\n    '''触觉伺服控制器\n    \n    用触觉图像引导机器人调整:\n    - 接触位置 (对心)\n    - 法向力 (恒力控制)\n    - 切向力 (防滑)\n    '''\n    def __init__(self, target_force=2.0, target_center=(160, 120)):\n        self.target_force = target_force  # N\n        self.target_center = np.array(target_center)  # 像素\n        self.Kp_force = 0.001  # 力控增益\n        self.Kp_pos = 0.0001  # 位置控增益\n    \n    def compute_contact_centroid(self, depth_image):\n        '''从触觉深度图计算接触质心'''\n        contact_mask = depth_image > 0.1  # 接触区域\n        if not np.any(contact_mask):\n            return None, 0\n        ys, xs = np.where(contact_mask)\n        centroid = np.array([xs.mean(), ys.mean()])\n        area = len(xs)\n        return centroid, area\n    \n    def estimate_force(self, depth_image):\n        '''从形变量估计法向力 (简化: F ~ k * deformation)'''\n        max_deformation = np.max(depth_image)\n        k_stiffness = 50.0  # N/mm 弹性体刚度\n        return k_stiffness * max_deformation / 1000  # N\n    \n    def servo(self, depth_image):\n        '''触觉伺服: 输出末端速度修正\n        \n        Returns: (dz, dx, dy) 末端速度修正\n        '''\n        # 力控: 调整z方向保持恒定法向力\n        current_force = self.estimate_force(depth_image)\n        force_error = self.target_force - current_force\n        dz = self.Kp_force * force_error  # 力不够→压下去, 力太大→抬起来\n        \n        # 位置控: 调整xy保持接触居中\n        centroid, area = self.compute_contact_centroid(depth_image)\n        dx, dy = 0, 0\n        if centroid is not None:\n            pos_error = self.target_center - centroid\n            dx = self.Kp_pos * pos_error[0]\n            dy = self.Kp_pos * pos_error[1]\n        \n        return np.array([dx, dy, dz])\n\n# 模拟\nctrl = TactileServoController(target_force=2.0)\n\n# 模拟触觉图像 (320x240深度图)\nfor step in range(5):\n    depth = np.zeros((240, 320))\n    # 模拟偏心接触\n    cx, cy = 180 + step*5, 130 + step*3\n    Y, X = np.ogrid[:240, :320]\n    contact = ((X-cx)**2 + (Y-cy)**2 < 30**2)\n    depth[contact] = 0.03 + step*0.005  # 形变量递增\n    \n    vel = ctrl.servo(depth)\n    force = ctrl.estimate_force(depth)\n    centroid, _ = ctrl.compute_contact_centroid(depth)\n    \n    print(f'Step {step}: force={force:.2f}N, '\n          f'centroid=({centroid[0]:.0f},{centroid[1]:.0f}), '\n          f'correction=({vel[0]:.4f},{vel[1]:.4f},{vel[2]:.4f})')\n```\n\n### 练习\n1. 用DIGIT/GelSight传感器实现触觉伺服peg-in-hole\n2. 实现基于触觉的恒力表面跟随控制\n3. 结合视觉+触觉的双模态伺服：视觉粗定位→触觉精细调整"},
    {"file": "probability-statistics.json", "title": "隐马尔可夫模型(HMM)与机器人行为识别",
     "content": "### HMM在机器人中的应用\n\n**隐马尔可夫模型(HMM)**是时序数据建模的经典方法。在机器人中用于：\n- 行为识别：从传感器序列识别当前在做什么\n- 故障检测：从振动/声音序列检测异常状态\n- 手势识别：从手部轨迹识别操作员意图\n\n### HMM三要素\n\n```\n隐状态 S: {行走, 抓取, 搬运, 放置}  (不直接观测)\n观测 O:   传感器读数序列            (直接观测)\n参数 lambda = (A, B, pi):\n  A: 状态转移概率 P(s_t | s_{t-1})\n  B: 发射概率 P(o_t | s_t)\n  pi: 初始状态概率\n\n三个基本问题:\n  1. 评估: P(O|lambda) → 前向算法\n  2. 解码: argmax P(S|O,lambda) → Viterbi算法\n  3. 学习: argmax P(O|lambda) → Baum-Welch(EM)\n```\n\n```python\nimport numpy as np\n\nclass SimpleHMM:\n    '''隐马尔可夫模型 (前向算法 + Viterbi解码)'''\n    \n    def __init__(self, n_states, n_obs):\n        self.n_states = n_states\n        self.n_obs = n_obs\n        # 随机初始化参数\n        self.A = np.random.dirichlet(np.ones(n_states), n_states)  # 转移矩阵\n        self.B = np.random.dirichlet(np.ones(n_obs), n_states)     # 发射矩阵\n        self.pi = np.random.dirichlet(np.ones(n_states))           # 初始概率\n    \n    def forward(self, observations):\n        '''前向算法: 计算P(O|lambda)'''\n        T = len(observations)\n        alpha = np.zeros((T, self.n_states))\n        # 初始化\n        alpha[0] = self.pi * self.B[:, observations[0]]\n        # 递推\n        for t in range(1, T):\n            for j in range(self.n_states):\n                alpha[t, j] = np.sum(alpha[t-1] * self.A[:, j]) * self.B[j, observations[t]]\n        return np.sum(alpha[-1])  # P(O|lambda)\n    \n    def viterbi(self, observations):\n        '''Viterbi算法: 找最可能的状态序列'''\n        T = len(observations)\n        delta = np.zeros((T, self.n_states))\n        psi = np.zeros((T, self.n_states), dtype=int)\n        # 初始化\n        delta[0] = self.pi * self.B[:, observations[0]]\n        # 递推\n        for t in range(1, T):\n            for j in range(self.n_states):\n                probs = delta[t-1] * self.A[:, j]\n                psi[t, j] = np.argmax(probs)\n                delta[t, j] = probs[psi[t, j]] * self.B[j, observations[t]]\n        # 回溯\n        states = np.zeros(T, dtype=int)\n        states[-1] = np.argmax(delta[-1])\n        for t in range(T-2, -1, -1):\n            states[t] = psi[t+1, states[t+1]]\n        return states\n\n# 机器人行为识别示例\nstate_names = ['idle', 'reaching', 'grasping', 'placing']\nobs_names = ['low_vel', 'high_vel', 'contact', 'no_contact']\n\nhmm = SimpleHMM(n_states=4, n_obs=4)\n# 设定合理的转移概率\nhmm.A = np.array([\n    [0.7, 0.3, 0.0, 0.0],  # idle -> idle/reaching\n    [0.0, 0.5, 0.5, 0.0],  # reaching -> reaching/grasping\n    [0.0, 0.0, 0.6, 0.4],  # grasping -> grasping/placing\n    [0.5, 0.0, 0.0, 0.5],  # placing -> idle/placing\n])\nhmm.B = np.array([\n    [0.8, 0.1, 0.05, 0.05],  # idle: 低速+无接触\n    [0.1, 0.7, 0.05, 0.15],  # reaching: 高速\n    [0.1, 0.1, 0.7, 0.1],    # grasping: 接触\n    [0.1, 0.5, 0.1, 0.3],    # placing: 高速+无接触\n])\nhmm.pi = np.array([0.8, 0.1, 0.05, 0.05])\n\n# 模拟观测序列\nobservations = [0, 0, 1, 1, 2, 2, 2, 1, 0, 0]  # 低速→高速→接触→高速→低速\nstates = hmm.viterbi(observations)\nprob = hmm.forward(observations)\n\nprint('机器人行为识别 (HMM Viterbi解码):')\nprint(f'观测序列: {[obs_names[o] for o in observations]}')\nprint(f'状态序列: {[state_names[s] for s in states]}')\nprint(f'序列概率: {prob:.6e}')\n```\n\n### 练习\n1. 用HMM识别机器人的操作阶段(到达/抓取/搬运/放置)\n2. 实现Baum-Welch算法从无标注数据学习HMM参数\n3. 对比HMM和LSTM在行为识别任务上的准确率"},
    {"file": "python-scientific-computing.json", "title": "并行计算：multiprocessing与Ray加速数据处理",
     "content": "### Python的GIL困境与解决方案\n\nPython的全局解释器锁(GIL)限制了多线程的CPU并行。机器人数据处理（图像增强、点云处理、轨迹计算）需要真正的并行加速。\n\n### 方案对比\n\n| 方案 | 适用 | 加速比 | 复杂度 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|\n| **multiprocessing** | 单机多核 | ~核数 | 低 |\n| **Ray** | 单机/集群 | ~核数/节点数 | 中 |\n| **Dask** | 大数据 | ~核数 | 中 |\n| **NumPy向量化** | 数值计算 | 10-100x | 低 |\n\n```python\nimport numpy as np\nimport time\nfrom multiprocessing import Pool\nfrom concurrent.futures import ProcessPoolExecutor\n\ndef process_episode(episode_data):\n    '''处理单条轨迹 (CPU密集)'''\n    images, actions = episode_data\n    # 模拟图像处理\n    processed = []\n    for img in images:\n        # 随机裁剪+归一化+增强\n        augmented = img * np.random.uniform(0.8, 1.2) + np.random.randn(*img.shape) * 0.01\n        processed.append(augmented)\n    return np.array(processed), actions\n\ndef benchmark_serial_vs_parallel(n_episodes=100, n_frames=50):\n    '''对比串行和并行处理速度'''\n    # 创建模拟数据\n    episodes = []\n    for _ in range(n_episodes):\n        images = [np.random.randn(84, 84, 3).astype(np.float32) for _ in range(n_frames)]\n        actions = np.random.randn(n_frames, 7).astype(np.float32)\n        episodes.append((images, actions))\n    \n    # 串行处理\n    t0 = time.perf_counter()\n    results_serial = [process_episode(ep) for ep in episodes]\n    t_serial = time.perf_counter() - t0\n    \n    # 并行处理 (multiprocessing)\n    t0 = time.perf_counter()\n    with ProcessPoolExecutor(max_workers=4) as executor:\n        results_parallel = list(executor.map(process_episode, episodes))\n    t_parallel = time.perf_counter() - t0\n    \n    print(f'数据处理 ({n_episodes} episodes x {n_frames} frames):')\n    print(f'  串行: {t_serial:.2f}s')\n    print(f'  并行(4进程): {t_parallel:.2f}s')\n    print(f'  加速比: {t_serial/t_parallel:.1f}x')\n\nbenchmark_serial_vs_parallel(n_episodes=20, n_frames=10)\n\n# Ray分布式处理 (概念)\nprint('\\nRay分布式处理 (概念):')\nprint('  import ray')\nprint('  ray.init()')\nprint('  @ray.remote')\nprint('  def process_episode_remote(ep): ...')\nprint('  futures = [process_episode_remote.remote(ep) for ep in episodes]')\nprint('  results = ray.get(futures)')\nprint('  → 自动分发到多核/多机, API与单机几乎一样')\n```\n\n### 练习\n1. 用multiprocessing加速LeRobot数据集的图像增强\n2. 用Ray实现分布式超参数搜索\n3. 对比vectorized NumPy和multiprocessing在不同数据规模下的效率"},
    {"file": "ros2.json", "title": "DDS通信调优与QoS策略选择",
     "content": "### DDS是ROS2的通信基础\n\nROS2底层使用DDS(Data Distribution Service)中间件进行通信。不同的QoS(Quality of Service)配置直接影响数据传输的可靠性和延迟。\n\n### QoS策略选择指南\n\n| 数据类型 | 可靠性 | 持久性 | 历史 | 原因 |\n|---------|--------|--------|------|------|\n| 相机图像 | BestEffort | Volatile | KeepLast(1) | 丢帧可接受，要最新 |\n| 控制指令 | Reliable | Volatile | KeepLast(1) | 不能丢，要最新 |\n| 地图数据 | Reliable | TransientLocal | KeepLast(1) | 新订阅者需要最新地图 |\n| 日志 | BestEffort | Volatile | KeepAll | 尽量收集，丢了也行 |\n| TF变换 | Reliable | Volatile | KeepLast(10) | 需要最近几帧用于插值 |\n\n### QoS不匹配 = 收不到消息\n\n```\n最常见的ROS2通信问题:\n  Publisher: Reliable\n  Subscriber: BestEffort\n  → 可以通信 (宽松订阅严格发布)\n\n  Publisher: BestEffort  \n  Subscriber: Reliable\n  → 无法通信! (严格订阅宽松发布)\n  \n  解决: ros2 topic info /topic --verbose 查看QoS\n```\n\n```python\nimport time\nimport numpy as np\n\nclass QoSSimulator:\n    '''模拟不同QoS策略对通信的影响'''\n    \n    def __init__(self):\n        self.configs = {\n            'camera_stream': {\n                'reliability': 'best_effort',\n                'history': 'keep_last',\n                'depth': 1,\n                'description': '相机图像: 丢帧可接受，低延迟优先',\n            },\n            'control_command': {\n                'reliability': 'reliable',\n                'history': 'keep_last',\n                'depth': 1,\n                'description': '控制指令: 不能丢，保证送达',\n            },\n            'map_update': {\n                'reliability': 'reliable',\n                'history': 'keep_last',\n                'depth': 1,\n                'durability': 'transient_local',\n                'description': '地图: 新订阅者能收到最新地图',\n            },\n        }\n    \n    def simulate_transmission(self, config_name, n_messages=100,\n                              network_loss_rate=0.05, network_delay_ms=5):\n        '''模拟消息传输'''\n        config = self.configs[config_name]\n        reliable = config['reliability'] == 'reliable'\n        \n        received = 0\n        total_delay = 0\n        retransmissions = 0\n        \n        for i in range(n_messages):\n            delay = network_delay_ms + np.random.exponential(2)  # 随机延迟\n            lost = np.random.random() < network_loss_rate\n            \n            if lost and reliable:\n                # Reliable: 重传\n                retransmissions += 1\n                delay += network_delay_ms * 2  # 重传延迟\n                received += 1\n            elif lost:\n                # BestEffort: 丢弃\n                continue\n            else:\n                received += 1\n            \n            total_delay += delay\n        \n        avg_delay = total_delay / max(received, 1)\n        print(f'{config_name}:')\n        print(f'  QoS: {config[\"reliability\"]}')\n        print(f'  收到: {received}/{n_messages} ({received/n_messages:.0%})')\n        print(f'  平均延迟: {avg_delay:.1f}ms')\n        print(f'  重传次数: {retransmissions}')\n        print(f'  → {config[\"description\"]}')\n\nsim = QoSSimulator()\nprint('QoS策略仿真 (5%丢包率):')\nfor name in sim.configs:\n    sim.simulate_transmission(name)\n    print()\n\nprint('ROS2 QoS常用命令:')\nprint('  ros2 topic info /topic --verbose  # 查看QoS')\nprint('  ros2 topic echo /topic --qos-reliability best_effort')\nprint('  ros2 topic hz /topic              # 查看实际频率')\n```\n\n### 练习\n1. 调试一个QoS不匹配导致收不到消息的问题\n2. 对比Reliable和BestEffort在高丢包环境下的表现\n3. 为一个完整的机械臂系统配置所有topic的QoS策略"}
]

for update in UPDATES:
    filepath = BASE + update["file"]
    with open(filepath, "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        data = json.load(f)
    existing_titles = [s.get("title","") for s in data.get("sections", [])]
    if update["title"] in existing_titles:
        print(f"SKIP {update['file']}: already exists")
        continue
    new_section = {"title": update["title"], "lastUpdated": TIMESTAMP, "content": update["content"]}
    data["sections"].append(new_section)
    data["lastUpdated"] = TIMESTAMP
    with open(filepath, "w", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        json.dump(data, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)
    print(f"OK {update['file']}: +'{update['title']}' ({len(data['sections'])}sec)")

lp = "data/learning-path.json"
